<div class="header">
    <h1>AnyLeft</h1>
    <h2>Household item-tracking made easy</h2>
</div>

<div class="content has-centered-text">
    <h2 class="content-subhead">How it works</h2>

    <div class="pure-g">
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/no1.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/shampoo.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/text-field-rename.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">Enter the name and size of the item you want to track.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/no2.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/shower.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/solid-plus.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">Each time you use the item, simply hit the 'Used It' button.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/no3.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/solid-ok.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">When you run out, hit the 'All&nbsp;out!' button.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/no4.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/shampoo.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/calendar-week.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">When using that product again in the future, AnyLeft will predict how many uses are left based on your behavior, even projecting when it will be depleted.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="highlight"></div>

    <h2 class="content-subhead">Track Almost Anything</h2>
    <div class="pure-g">
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/soap.png" />
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/lotion.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">Track regular-use items such as hygiene or personal care products easily.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/pizza.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">Great for determining just how long those left overs last, and if it's worth keeping half the pie for yourself.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/beer.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">Get a heads up when you need to make a beer run, before it's too late.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="content-subhead">Super Low Effort</h2>
    <div class="pure-g">
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/mug.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">One button. Two, max. We want to keep the process simple so tracking isn't a chore, and you can focus on what you want to.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
            <img class="pure-img-responsive" src="assets/img/icons/calendar-day.png" />
            <p class="home-blurb">The more you track an item, the more accurate AnyLeft's predictions become on projected depletion dates.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{> global/signup-cta}}

</div>